formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	Sale value of the unsold property taken as certify by the management.							
2	Estimated construction value of the project taken as certify by the engineer.							
3	Technical measurement taken as provided by the management.							
4	Actual cost taken as per books of accounts up to 31.12.2019							
5	The Cost of the project not registered with RERA (as BU received before RERA) has been excluded from cost of project registered with RERA as per allocation given by the management of the firm.							
6	Since no separate account of 100% and 70% as per RERA is maintained, withdrawal at point no. 7 at page no. 2 has been computed directly 70% of amount received from the customer.							
7	The opening balance for RERA A/C as on 01/09/2019 is Rs.134232. However, there was mistake in previous return due to oversight of assistant and the same has been adjusted in deposits in current period.
